MISHKAKI & MCHICHA

INGREDIENTS

Beef
Onion
Garlic Ginger Paste
Lemon Juice
Soy Sauce
Garam Masala
Curry Powder
Chili powder
Pepper
Salt 
Oil


PREP

Show Garam Masala
Show Curry Powder
Show Chili Powder
Pour Soy Sauce
Pour Oil
Juice Lemon
Open Coconut Milk
Separate Coconut Cream
Mince Garlic
Mince Ginger
Slice Onion
Chop Amaranth
Slice Tomato

Cut Beef
Beef in Bowl
Add Ginger
Add Garlic
Add Oil
Add Soy Sauce
Add Lemon Juice
Add Garam Masala
Add Curry Powder
Add Chili Powder
Add Salt
Add Pepper

Marinate for 2 Hrs

COOK

Add Meat to Skewers
Place in Toaster
Toast

Add Amaranth to Pot
Add Onions
Add Tomatoes
Cook Until Amaranth Releases Water
Add Coconut Milk

Serve